---
// Hero.astro — Nobu
// Hero minimalista: fondo sólido, título, párrafo y botón.
---

<section class="relative flex min-h-screen items-center justify-center bg-[#0D0D0D] px-4 py-24 sm:py-28 md:py-32 text-center">
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-3xl flex-col items-center">
    <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl">
      Nobu
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl text-base text-white/80 sm:text-lg md:text-xl">
      Creamos sitios web modernos, claros y adaptados a tu marca.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8">
      <a
        href="#contacto"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-2xl bg-blue-500 px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-[#0D0D0D] shadow-lg transition hover:bg-blue-400 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-blue-400"
      >
        Contáctanos
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
